l%20vision%20for%20the%20epic%20saga.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftelugu%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Frana-daggubati-reveals-he-was-not-the-first-choice-for-bhallaladeva-in-the-historic-epic-baahubali%2Farticleshow%2F112240988.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Small%20entertainers%20dominated%20the%20first%20half%20of%202024!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722666600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112222663%2Cimgsize-74202.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsmall-budget-movies-dominate-first-half-of-2024%2Farticleshow%2F112221932.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112221932.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20half%20of%202024%20saw%20small-budget%20films%20with%20compelling%20narratives%20outperforming%20big-budget%20movies%20with%20lesser-known%20stars%20drawing%20audiences.%20Horror%20films%20like%20Munjya%20and%20Aranmanai%204%20were%20notably%20successful.%20Director%20Aditya%20Sarpotdar%20emphasized%20the%20broad%20appeal%20and%20cost-effectiveness%20of%20horror.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Bharti%20Dubey%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsmall-budget-movies-dominate-first-half-of-2024%2Farticleshow%2F112221932.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEither%20Bullets%20Will%20Be%20Fired%20Or...%26quot%3B%3A%20New%20Detail%20In%20Salman%20Khan%20House%20Firing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20detailed%20chargesheet%20shedding%20light%20on%20the%20events%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20attack%20on%20Bollywood%20actor%20Salman%20Khan's%20residence%20in%20April%20reveals%20a%20long%20conversation%20between%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%2C%20the%20brother%20of%20the%20incarcerated%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%2C%20and%20the%20shooters%20involved.%20A%209-minute-long%20speech%20by%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%20was%20aimed%20at%20instilling%20courage%20in%20the%20shooters%2C%20Vicky%20Gupta%20and%20Sagar%20Pal%2C%20as%20they%20prepared%20to%20%26quot%3Bscript%20history%26quot%3B%20with%20their%20violent%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20night%20of%20April%2014%2C%20Mumbai's%20Bandra%20neighbourhood%20was%20rocked%20by%20the%20sound%20of%20gunfire%20as%20two%20men%20on%20motorbikes%20fired%20multiple%20rounds%20outside%20Salman%20Khan's%20residence.%20This%20brazen%20attack%20led%20to%20a%20swift%20police%20response%20and%20the%20subsequent%20arrest%20of%20several%20individuals%20linked%20to%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnmol%20Bishnoi's%20Speech%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nine-minute%20audio%20clip%20begins%20with%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%20giving%20a%20pep%20talk%2C%20with%20religious%20references%2C%20to%20the%20shooters.%20%26quot%3BLord%20Ram%20has%20blessed%20us.%20We%20will%20handle%20(Salman%20Khan)%20him.%20There%20is%20no%20problem%2C%20as%20long%20as%20it%20is%20in%20my%20control%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20it%20is%20do%20or%20die%2C%20either%20life%20or%20death.%20It%20is%20written%20by%20God.%20Either%20the%20bullets%20will%20be%20fired%20in%20the%20morning%20or%20we%20will%20sit%20at%20home.%20It%20is%20in%20your%20hands%20what%20to%20do%20and%20what%20not%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%20said.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BIf%20you%20work%2C%20then%20history%20will%20be%20created.%20You%20will%20fill%20the%20newspapers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20chargesheet%2C%20the%20plan%20was%20hatched%20over%20several%20months%2C%20from%20August%202023%20to%20April%202024.%20Investigations%20have%20revealed%20that%20the%20gang%20intended%20to%20acquire%20advanced%20firearms%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20including%20AK-47s%2C%20AK-92s%2C%20M16%20rifles%2C%20and%20the%20Turkish-made%20Zigana%20pistol%2C%20the%20weapon%20used%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20Punjabi%20singer%20Sidhu%20Moose%20Wala%20on%20May%2029%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20be%20afraid%20at%20all%20while%20doing%20this%20work.%20Doing%20this%20work%20means%20bringing%20change%20in%20the%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%20said.%20He%20told%20the%20shooters%20that%20the%20Bishnoi%20Gang%20had%20a%20signature%20move.%20According%20to%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%2C%20whenever%20the%20gang%20attempts%20a%20killing%2C%20they%20empty%20the%20magazine%20of%20the%20gun.%20%26quot%3BYou%20people%20will%20empty%20the%20magazine%20as%20soon%20as%20you%20reach%20outside%20Salman%20Khan's%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Operation%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20chargesheet%2C%20a%20network%20of%20approximately%2060%20to%2070%20individuals%20was%20involved%20in%20tracking%20Mr%20Khan's%20every%20movement.%20This%20extensive%20surveillance%20covered%20his%20residence%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20his%20Panvel%20farmhouse%2C%20and%20even%20the%20Goregaon%20Film%20City%2C%20where%20he%20often%20visited%20for%20film%20shoots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chargesheet%20claims%20that%20boys%20below%20the%20age%20of%2018%20were%20recruited%20to%20execute%20the%20assassination.%20These%20minors%20were%20reportedly%20waiting%20for%20orders%20from%20Goldie%20Brar%20and%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20operating%20from%20North%20America%2C%20to%20initiate%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20a%20special%20court%20in%20Mumbai%20issued%20a%20non-bailable%20warrant%20(NBW)%20against%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%20and%20Rohit%20Godera%2C%20an%20alleged%20member%20of%20the%20Bishnoi%20gang.%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20is%20currently%20lodged%20in%20the%20Sabarmati%20central%20prison%20in%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722666000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fk9b2vlj_salman-khan_625x300_26_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsalman-khan-anmol-bishnoi-lawrence-bishnoi-empty-the-magazine-outside-salman-khans-home-shooters-were-told-6253326%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20detailed%20chargesheet%20shedding%20light%20on%20the%20events%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20attack%20on%20Bollywood%20actor%20Salman%20Khan's%20residence%20in%20April%20reveals%20a%20long%20conversation%20between%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%20and%20the%20shooters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsalman-khan-anmol-bishnoi-lawrence-bishnoi-empty-the-magazine-outside-salman-khans-home-shooters-were-told-6253326%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsalman-khan-anmol-bishnoi-lawrence-bishnoi-empty-the-magazine-outside-salman-khans-home-shooters-were-told-6253326%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsalman-khan-anmol-bishnoi-lawrence-bishnoi-empty-the-magazine-outside-salman-khans-home-shooters-were-told-6253326%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tropical%20storm%20brewing%3A%20Emergency%20declared%20in%20Florida%20as%20heavy%20rain%2C%20strong%20winds%20expected%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722665979000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112238730%2Cimgsize-1706374.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftropical-storm-brewing-emergency-declared-in-florida-as-heavy-rain-strong-winds-expected%2Farticleshow%2F112238735.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D