nowballing%20into%20a%20massive%20controversy%2C%20the%2078-year-old%20doubled%20down%20and%20shared%20a%20picture%20on%20social%20media%20which%20shows%20Kamala%20Harris'%20%26quot%3BIndian%20heritage%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThank%20you%20Kamala%20for%20the%20nice%20picture%20you%20sent%20from%20many%20years%20ago!%20Your%20warmth%2C%20friendship%2C%20and%20love%20of%20your%20Indian%20Heritage%20are%20very%20much%20appreciated%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20while%20sharing%20the%20photo%20on%20Truth%20Social.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2F112887108527191005%2Fembed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20a%20history%20of%20attacking%20his%20opponents%20based%20on%20race.%20He%20falsely%20accused%20Barack%20Obama%2C%20the%20country's%20first%20black%20president%2C%20of%20not%20being%20born%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20attacked%20the%20former%20UN%20ambassador%20and%20his%20Republican%20primary%20opponent%20Nikki%20Haley%20by%20falsely%20claiming%20she%20could%20not%20be%20president%20because%20her%20parents%20were%20not%20US%20citizens%20when%20she%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%2C%20Kamala%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamala%20Harris'%20mother%2C%20Shyamala%20Gopalan%2C%20was%20Indian%20and%20her%20father%2C%20Donald%20Jasper%20Harris%2C%20is%20Jamaican%3B%20both%20immigrated%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20seeking%20to%20become%20the%20first%20Black%20woman%20and%20Asian-American%20president%20in%20US%20history%20and%20her%20entry%20into%20the%202024%20contest%20has%20seen%20a%20surge%20of%20enthusiasm%20for%20her%20candidacy%20among%20Black%20voters%20and%20young%20people%20%E2%80%94%20groups%20with%20which%20Trump%20has%20sought%20to%20broaden%20his%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20controversial%20remarks%20come%20as%20the%20race%20for%20the%20November%205%20presidential%20election%20gained%20momentum%20with%20opinion%20polls%20showing%20that%20Vice%20President%20Harris%2C%20abruptly%20thrust%20into%20the%20role%20of%20presidential%20candidate%20fewer%20than%2010%20days%20ago%2C%20has%20narrowed%20the%20gap%20with%20her%20Republican%20rival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20condemned%20Trump's%20comments%20later%20Wednesday%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20same%20old%20show%E2%80%9D%20of%20%26quot%3Bdivisiveness%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdisrespect%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20me%20just%20say%3A%20The%20American%20people%20deserve%20better.%20The%20American%20people%20deserve%20better%20than%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Harris%20said%20during%20a%20speech%20to%20a%20historically%20Black%20sorority%20convention%20in%20Houston.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20July%20Bloomberg%20News%2FMorning%20Consult%20poll%20released%20Tuesday%20showed%20Harris%20erased%20the%20lead%20Trump%20enjoyed%20in%20seven%20states%20likely%20to%20determine%20the%20election%2C%20leading%20the%20former%20president%2048%25%20to%2047%25%20%E2%80%94%20a%20statistical%20tie.%20The%20survey%20also%20showed%20that%20across%20those%20states%2C%20Harris%20enjoyed%20the%20support%20of%2075%25%20of%20Black%20voters%2C%20compared%20to%2019%25%20for%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722663660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fugf3uu1g_trump-harris-_625x300_22_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-attacks-kamala-harris-black-indian-identity-as-presidential-polls-near-6253238%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20the%20US%20Presidential%20election%20in%20its%20last%20stretch%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Kamala%20Harris%20are%20leaving%20no%20stone%20turned%20to%20win%20voters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-attacks-kamala-harris-black-indian-identity-as-preside