ombs%20In%203%20Rooms%3A%20Inside%20Mossad's%20Kill%20Op%20For%20Hamas%20Chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20elite%20intelligence%20agency%20Mossad%20enlisted%20Iranian%20security%20agents%20to%20plant%20explosives%20in%20a%20building%20in%20Tehran%20where%20armed%20Palestinian%20group%20Hamas's%20political%20leader%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20was%20staying%2C%20The%20Telegraph%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fworld-news%2F2024%2F08%2F02%2Fmossad-hired-iranian-agents-to-plant-bombs-haniyeh-rooms%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20plan%20was%20to%20assassinate%20Haniyeh%20in%20May%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20Tehran%20for%20the%20funeral%20of%20former%20Iranian%20President%20Ebrahim%20Raisi.%20The%20operation%20was%20aborted%20due%20to%20overwhelming%20crowds%2C%20which%20posed%20a%20major%20risk%20of%20failure%2C%20according%20to%20two%20Iranian%20officials%20who%20spoke%20to%20The%20Telegraph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20operation%20had%20to%20be%20modified.%20Two%20agents%2C%20working%20under%20Mossad's%20direction%2C%20placed%20explosive%20devices%20in%20three%20separate%20rooms%20of%20the%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20(IRGC)%20guesthouse%20in%20northern%20Tehran.%20This%20location%20was%20strategically%20chosen%20as%20it%20was%20likely%20that%20Haniyeh%20would%20stay%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Mossad%20Functions%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20%243%20billion%20annual%20budget%20and%207%2C000-strong%20staff%2C%20Mossad%20is%20the%20second-largest%20espionage%20agency%20in%20the%20West%20after%20the%20CIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMossad%20has%20several%20departments%2C%20but%20the%20details%20of%20its%20internal%20structure%20are%20mostly%20hidden.%20It%20not%20only%20has%20a%20network%20of%20informants%20and%20agents%20inside%20Palestinian%20militant%20groups%2C%20but%20also%20in%20hostile%20countries%20like%20Lebanon%2C%20Syria%2C%20and%20Iran.%20The%20intelligence%20agency's%20vast%20spy%20network%20provides%20them%20with%20intimate%20knowledge%20of%20militant%20leaders'%20movements%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20execute%20precise%20assassinations%20as%20and%20when%20necessitated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExplained%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-mossad-gaza-hamas-attackexplained-how-mossad-functions-and-how-it-failed-to-stop-hamas-attack-4463289%5C%22%3EHow%20Mossad%20Functions%20And%20Why%20It%20Failed%20To%20Stop%20Hamas%20Attack%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Special%20Operations%20Division%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Metsada%2C%20carries%20out%20highly%20sensitive%20assassinations%2C%20sabotage%2C%20paramilitary%2C%20and%20psychological%20warfare%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOperation%20To%20Eliminate%20Haniyeh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20The%20Telegraph%2C%20surveillance%20footage%2C%20held%20by%20Iranian%20officials%2C%20shows%20the%20agents%20moving%20stealthily%2C%20entering%20and%20exiting%20multiple%20rooms%20within%20minutes.%20After%20planting%20the%20devices%2C%20they%20exited%20Iran%20undetected%20but%20maintained%20a%20source%20within%20the%20country.%20In%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Wednesday%2C%20at%202%20am%2C%20the%20operatives%20remotely%20detonated%20the%20explosives%20in%20the%20room%20where%20Haniyeh%20was%20staying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20explosion%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20Haniyeh%2C%20who%20was%20in%20Tehran%20to%20attend%20the%20inauguration%20of%20President%20Masoud%20Pezeshkian.%20This%20assassination%20has%20been%20confirmed%20by%20officials%20within%20the%20IRGC%2C%20who%20now%20believe%20Mossad%20employed%20agents%20from%20the%20Ansar-al-Mahdi%20protection%20unit%2C%20a%20group%20responsible%20for%20safeguarding%20high-ranking%20officials%20inside%20and%20outside%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20humiliation%20for%20Iran%20and%20a%20huge%20security%20breach%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20IRGC%20official%20told%20The%20Telegraph.%20A%20special%20working%20group%20has%20been%20established%20to%20devise%20strategies%20to%20mitigate%20the%20perception%20of%20this%20breach%2C%20the%20official%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPotential%20Ramifications%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20this%20breach%2C%20the%20IRGC%20is%20considering%20its%20options%20for%20retaliation.%20A%20direct%20strike%20on%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20potentially%20involving%20Hezbollah%20and%20other%20Iranian%20proxies%2C%20is%20reportedly%20a%20primary%20option%20under%20evaluation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Islamic%20Revolution%20of%201979%20that%20upended%20Iran's%20political%20and%20societal%20structure%2C%20the%20country%20has%20made%20a%20conscious%20effort%20to%20fan%20its%20influence%20across%20the%20Middle%20East%20with%20proxy%20groups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExplained%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-palestine-gaza-explained-axis-of-resistance-and-irans-proxy-network-across-middle-east-4534061%5C%22%3EAxis%20Of%20Resistance%20And%20Iran's%20Proxy%20Network%20Across%20Middle%20East%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Quds%20Force%2C%20one%20of%20the%20five%20branches%20of%20the%20IRGC%2C%20which%20specialises%20in%20intelligence%20and%20covert%20operations%2C%20serves%20as%20the%20main%20point%20of%20contact%20for%20these%20proxy%20groups%2C%20providing%20them%20with%20weapons%20and%20training%20to%20solidify%20Iran's%20regional%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20timing%20of%20the%20assassination%2C%20coinciding%20with%20President%20Pezeshkian's%20first%20day%20in%20office%2C%20has%20sparked%20suspicions%20about%20its%20intentionality.%20During%20his%20campaign%2C%20President%20Pezeshkian%20had%20pledged%20to%20move%20away%20from%20the%20Islamic%20Republic's%20provocative%20policies%20and%20to%20restore%20Iran's%20standing%20through%20dialogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Pezeshkian%2C%20a%20seasoned%20lawmaker%20and%20cardiac%20surgeon%2C%20has%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmasoud-pezeshkian-iran-has-a-new-reformist-president-what-it-would-mean-for-india-6045285%5C%22%3E%20long%20supported%20both%20domestic%20and%20international%20reforms%20in%20Iran%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20win%20in%20the%20recent%20elections%20is%20viewed%20as%20a%20call%20for%20change%20since%20it%20follows%20a%20general%20unhappiness%20with%20the%20hardline%20policies%20of%20his%20predecessors.%20But%20the%20dynamics%20of%20Iranian%20politics%2C%20where%20hardliners%20still%20control%20the%20majority%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%20retains%20ultimate%20authority%2C%20will%20put%20Mr%20Pezeshkian's%20ability%20to%20carry%20out%20his%20vision%20to%20the%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722659220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F6g9a0lno_ismail-haniyeh-afp_625x300_03_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hired-iranian-agents-to-assassinate-hamas-chief-in-tehran-report-6252736%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel's%20elite%20intelligence%20agency%20Mossad%20enlisted%20Iranian%20security%20agents%20to%20plant%20explosives%20in%20a%20building%20in%20Tehran%20where%20armed%20Palestinian%20group%20Hamas's%20political%20leader%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20was%20staying%2C%20The%20Telegraph%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hired-iranian-agents-to-assassinate-hamas-chief-in-tehran-report-6252736%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hired-iranian-agents-to-assassinate-hamas-chief-in-tehran-report-6252736%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-new