illion%20in%20value%20in%20just%20over%20three%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestors%20have%20also%20become%20jittery%20over%20fears%20that%20this%20year's%20AI-fueled%20gains%20are%20overdone%20or%20the%20market%20is%20too%20concentrated.%20The%20decline%20in%20Amazon%20shares%20-%20the%20biggest%20drop%20since%20April%202022%20-%20came%20after%20the%20company%20said%20on%20an%20earnings%20call%20that%20it%20planned%20to%20continue%20spending%20big%20on%20AI%20even%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20short-term%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETechnology%20billionaires%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20Sergey%20Brin%20and%20Larry%20Page%20also%20each%20lost%20more%20than%20%243%20billion%20Friday%20as%20shares%20of%20Meta%20Platforms%20Inc.%20and%20Alphabet%20fell%20in%20New%20York%20trading.%20Tech%20tycoons%20in%20total%20saw%20%2468%20billion%20carved%20from%20their%20fortunes%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg's%20wealth%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBezos%2C%2060%2C%20the%20world's%20second-richest%20person%2C%20has%20been%20steadily%20offloading%20Amazon%20shares%20this%20year.%20He%20sold%20stock%20worth%20about%20%248.5%20billion%20over%20nine%20trading%20days%20in%20February.%20And%20on%20a%20day%20last%20month%20when%20Amazon%20hit%20a%20fresh%20record%2C%20he%20disclosed%20a%20plan%20to%20sell%2025%20million%20additional%20shares%20worth%20%245%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20additional%20sales%20would%20bring%20his%20total%20this%20year%20to%20roughly%20%2413.5%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg's%20calculations.%20He%20would%20still%20hold%20almost%20912%20million%20shares%2C%20or%20about%208.8%25%20of%20Amazon%2C%20once%20those%20sales%20are%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20wealth%20also%20derives%20from%20space-exploration%20company%20Blue%20Origin%20and%20the%20Washington%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722653700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F5jp369v8_jeff-bezos_625x300_03_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22h