he%20last%20ICC%20meeting%20has%20generated%20speculations%20that%20the%20back%20up%20funds%20have%20been%20kept%20in%20case%20India%20refuses%20to%20send%20its%20team%20to%20Pakistan%20and%20some%20matches%20have%20to%20be%20played%20at%20other%20venues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20said%20that%20indications%20are%20that%20additional%20amount%20of%20USD%204.5%20million%20is%20too%20meagre%20compared%20to%20the%20overall%20budget%20to%20cover%20moving%20matches%20from%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJay%20Shah%2C%20who%20also%20heads%20the%20Asian%20Cricket%20Council%2C%20was%20also%20in%20chair%20when%20the%20regional%20body%20recently%20decided%20to%20award%20the%20T20%20format%20Asia%20Cup%20in%202025%20to%20India%20and%20the%2050-over%20format%20Asia%20Cup%20in%202027%20to%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20said%20as%20per%20the%20tentative%20format%20for%20next%20year's%20Asia%20Cup%20again%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20are%20in%20same%20group%20and%20could%20potentially%20play%20a%20second%20time%20in%20the%20tournament's%20super%20four%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20third%20match%20could%20happen%20if%20they%20qualify%20for%20the%20final%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20disclosed%20that%20the%20ACC%20despite%20the%20confusion%20and%20late%20venue%20changes%20and%20extra%20expenses%20during%20the%20tournament%20had%20still%20managed%20to%20reap%20profits%20from%20the%202023%20Asia%20Cup%20held%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20profits%20came%20because%20of%20the%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20games.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722652620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fh11amgco_india-pakistan-afp_625x300_08_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Findia-to-face-pakistan-in-champions-trophy-2025-group-stage-report-makes-big-claim-6240813%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ICC%20has%20approved%