20Flip%206%2C%20like%20a%20premium%20design%20and%20a%20large%20cover%20display.%20The%20company%20built%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsamsung-galaxy-z-flip-5-review%23battery-life%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFlip%205's%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0excellent%20design%20and%20improved%20the%20metal%20frame's%20durability%20against%20shock%20and%20scuffs%20for%20the%20Flip%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%206%20folded%20held%20in%20a%20hand%2C%20showing%20its%20right%20edges%20with%20buttons.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a3e4ee1a227600e6320e7a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%206%20is%20a%20fetching%20little%20square%20when%20it's%20folded.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Flip%206%20is%20a%20sophisticated-looking%20device%20with%20its%20flat%20aluminum%20edges.%20I%20received%20a%20unit%20with%20the%20Silver%20Shadow%20color%20option%2C%20which%20gives%20the%20frost-textured%20rear%20glass%20and%20smooth%20metal%20frame%20an%20ultra-clean%20modern%20look.%20It's%20also%20available%20in%20more%20playful%20colors%2C%20like%20yellow%2C%20mint%2C%20and%20blue.%20Whatever%20color%20you%20go%20for%2C%20this%20thing%20looks%20gorgeous.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it's%20folded%2C%20the%20Flip%206%20is%20a%20square%20about%20twice%20as%20thick%20as%20a%20regular%20flat%20phone%2C%20but%20it%20takes%20up%20about%20half%20as%20much%20space.%20The%20cover%20display%20is%20black%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20color%20option%20you%20go%20for%2C%20except%20for%20the%20two%20rings%20around%20the%20camera%20that%20match%20the%20color%20you%20picked.%20The%20rear%20is%20glass%20with%20a%20smooth%20frosted%20texture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20rear%20of%20the%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%206%20held%20in%20a%20hand%20against%20a%20bamboo%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a3e540aab37011780af113%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUnfolded%2C%20the%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%206%20is%20a%20two-tone%20device%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20color%20you%20pick.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnfolded%2C%20the%20Flip%206%20looks%20and%20feels%20like%20a%20regular%20phone%2C%20and%20its%20hinge%20is%20strong%20enough%20to%20keep%20it%20flat%20when%20handling%20it%20like%20a%20regular%20phone%20%E2%80%94%20the%20hinge%20only%20starts%20to%20fold%20again%20if%20you%20give%20the%20Flip%20some%20spirited%20flicks%20of%20the%20wrist.%20There's%20still%20the%20tell-tale%20crease%20that%20spans%20the%20middle%20width%20of%20the%20display%2C%20but%20it's%20easy%20to%20ignore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20only%20complaint%20with%20the%20phone's%20look%20is%20that%20the%20black%20borders%20around%20the%20main%20display%20are%20thicker%20than%20those%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsamsung-galaxy-s24-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESamsung's%20Galaxy%20S24%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0series.%20When%20unfolded%2C%20the%20Flip%206%20has%20a%20narrower%20and%20taller%20design%20than%20a%20regular%20phone%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20content%20look%20smaller%20than%20it%20does%20on%20a%20typical%206.7-inch%20display.%20What%20you%20lose%20in%20width%2C%20you%20gain%20in%20height%2C%20and%20you%20can%20see%20more%20content%20in%20a%20web%20article%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20S24%20and%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%206%20shot%20side%20by%20side%2C%20focusing%20on%20the%20larger%20bezels%20on%20the%20Flip%206%2C%20as%20well%20as%20its%20narrower%20display.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a7ee85a0fc5856d5985ecc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%206%20has%20wider%20black%20borders%20around%20the%20display%20than%20the%20Galaxy%20S24.%20The%20Flip%206's%20display%20is%20also%20narrower%2C%20even%20though%20it%20has%20the%20same%206.7-inch%20display%20size%20as%20the%20Galaxy%20S24.%20The%20Flip%206%20also%20has%20%26quot%3BTrue%20Tone%26quot%3B%20enabled%20to%20make%20reading%20easier.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%C2%A0Another%20complaint%20is%20that%20unfolding%20the%20Flip%206%20can%20sometimes%20be%20an%20annoyance%2C%20mostly%20when%20my%20hands%20are%20busy%20with%20kids%20or%20groceries%2C%20or%20when%20I%20want%20to%20quickly%20take%20a%20photo%20before%20the%20moment%20dissipates.%20The%20hinge%20is%20so%20strong%20that%20opening%20it%20requires%20two%20hands%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can't%20flick%20it%20open%20like%20a%20retro%20flip%20phone.%3Cp%3ESamsung%20mitigates%20some%20of%20the%20inconveniences%20of%20unfolding%20the%20Flip%206%20with%20an%20exterior%20display%20on%20the%20cover%2C%20which%20is%20handy%20for%20quick%20little%20tasks%2C%20like%20replying%20to%20a%20message%2C%20checking%20notifications%2C%20controlling%20music%20playback%2C%20and%20getting%20quick%20bits%20of%20information%20from%20widgets%20like%20weather%2C%20calendar%2C%20reminder%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20box%2C%20you%20can%20run%20a%20very%20limited%20number%20of%20third-party%20apps%20on%20the%20cover%20screen.%20Yet%2C%20there%20is%20a%20way%20to%20make%20all%20of%20your%20apps%20available%2C%20which%20could%20make%20the%20Flip%206's%20cover%20screen%20infinitely%20more%20useful.%20It%20just%20requires%20a%20few%20extra%20steps%2C%20including%20installing%20the%20%26quot%3BGoodlock%26quot%3B%20app%20from%20the%20Galaxy%20app%20store%20and%20installing%20a%20module%20called%20%26quot%3BMultiStar%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20you're%20eventually%20given%20the%20option%20to%20run%20all%20your%20apps%20from%20the%20cover%20screen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20inescapable%20problem%20with%20the%20Flip%206%20is%20that%20it%20isn't%20dust-resistant%2C%20which%20could%20pose%20problems%20for%20the%20main%20display.%20If%20you're%20a%20beach-goer%20or%20visit%20dusty%20places%2C%20the%20Flip%206%20isn't%20for%20you.%20You%20could%20risk%20damaging%20it%2C%20like%20getting%20dust%20specks%20under%20the%20display%2C%20dents%20or%20bulges%2C%20or%20breaking%20the%20display.%20I%20went%20to%20a%20beach%20to%20test%20some%20phones%2C%20but%20I%20opted%20not%20to%20bring%20the%20Flip%206%20with%20me%20for%20this%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Performance%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPower%20you'd%20expect%20from%20a%20top%20processor%20and%20useful%20AI%20features%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20won't%20be%20starved%20for%20power%20and%20speed%20when%20running%20apps%20and%20games%20on%20the%20Flip%206.%20It%20runs%20on%20the%20Qualcomm%20Snapdragon%208%20Gen%203%20for%20Galaxy%20processor%2C%20the%20most%20powerful%20chip%20available%20for%20Android%20phones%20in%202024%2C%20and%20the%20same%20processor%20used%20in%20the%20flagship%20Galaxy%20S24%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%206%20unfolded%20held%20in%20a%20hand%20at%20an%20angle%20focusing%20the%20view%20on%20the%20phone's%20right%20edge%2C%20shot%20against%20a%20bamboo%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a3eca1aab37011780af486%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%206%20is%20as%20powerful%20as%20Android%20phones%20come%20in%202024.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Snapdragon%208%20Gen%203%20also%20powers%20Samsung's%20recently%20introduced%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsamsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-review%23ai-features%5C%22%3E%20Galaxy%20AI%20features%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Many%20of%20these%20features%20are%20centered%20on%20improving%20your%20photos%2C%20like%20deleting%20unwanted%20details%2C%20and%20niche%20functions%20like%20moving%20and%20resizing%20objects%2Fsubjects%20to%20different%20places.%20There%20are%20also%20AI-based%20translating%20features%20for%20calls%20and%20messages%2C%20webpage%20summarizing%2C%20wallpaper%20creation%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20Flip%206's%20new%20highlighted%20AI%20features%20is%20Suggested%20Replies%20for%20replying%20to%20messages%20from%20the%20cover%20display%2C%20and%20it%20gives%20you%20three%20reply%20options%20that%20are%20contextually%20relevant%20to%20a%20message%20you%20received.%20For%20example%2C%20when%20my%20wife%20told%20me%20she%20didn't%20feel%20well%2C%20Suggested%20Replies%20came%20up%20with%20%26quot%3BTake%20a%20rest%2C%20you'll%20feel%20better.%26quot%3B%20That's%20way%20beyond%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20usual%20quick%20replies%2C%20where%20the%20best%20option%20is%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20up%3F%26quot%3B%20Oddly%2C%20Suggested%20Replies%20isn't%20available%20when%20you're%20using%20the%20main%20display.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20the%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%206%20in%20the%20folded%20position%20showing%20its%20cover%20display%20with%20Samsung's%20AI%20Suggested%20Replies%20feautre%20making%20a%20suggestiong%20for%20a%20reply%20to%20a%20message.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66aa9e9c1a227600e6334f82%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESamsung's%20AI-based%20Suggested%20Replies%20creates%20much%20better%20replies%20to%20messages%20than%20the%20old%20quick%20replies.%3Cp%3