ange%20%E2%80%94%20battery%20life%20and%20camera%20performance.%20I%20used%20to%20be%20largely%20critical%20of%20Samsung's%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%20phones%2C%20but%20the%20Flip%206%20has%20won%20me%20over%2C%20and%20I'd%20happily%20include%20it%20in%20my%20shortlist%20of%20models%20for%20anyone%20who%20asks%20me%20which%20phone%20to%20buy%20next.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20I'd%20accompany%20my%20praises%20with%20notable%20concerns%2C%20like%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20don't%20feel%20comfortable%20bringing%20it%20to%20the%20beach%20or%20dusty%20places%20for%20the%20risk%20of%20damaging%20the%20screen.%20I'd%20also%20warn%20that%20the%20extra%20step%20of%20unfolding%20the%20phone%20felt%20cumbersome%2C%20but%20it%20might%20not%20be%20a%20dealbreaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsamsung-galaxy-z-flip-6-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722632797000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a3e0601a227600e6320c4a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsamsung-galaxy-z-flip-6-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Samsung's%20latest%20compact%20foldable%20phone%20for%202024%20is%20the%20Z%20Flip%206.%20Its%20longer%20battery%20life%20and%20powerful%20processor%20make%20it%20more%20viable%20for%20everyday%20use.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22avillasboas%40insider.com%20(Antonio%20Villas-Boas)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsamsung-galaxy-z-flip-6-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20New%20York%20Times%20and%20other%20top%20news%20sites%20block%20OpenAI's%20new%20SearchGPT%20web%20crawling%20bot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Altman%2C%20CEO%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20speaks%20at%20a%20conference%20in%20San%20Francisco%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ac21adb4912df3ae18668d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESam%20Altman%2C%20CEO%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20speaks%20at%20a%20conference%20in%20San%20Francisco%3Cp%3EANDREW%20CABALLERO-REYNOLDS%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20unveiled%20a%20new%20search%20engine%20called%20SearchGPT%20last%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESeveral%20top%20publisher%20sites%20are%20already%20blocking%20the%20related%20OpenAI%20web%20crawler%2C%20OAI-SearchBot.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20says%20this%20new%20bot%20doesn't%20collect%20data%20for%20AI%20model%20training.%20Some%20publishers%20probably%20don't%20believe%20that.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20week%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-gpt5-gpt4-expectations-ai-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20launched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-searchgpt-search-engine-prototype-declares-war-with-google-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESearchGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20some%20of%20the%20top%20news%20publishers%20have%20made%20clear%20they%20want%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20startup's%20new%20search%20engine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-accuses-new-york-times-hiring-someone-hack-its-products-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20at%20least%2013%20other%20news%20sites%20have%20blocked%20OAI-SearchBot.%20This%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-gptbot-web-crawler-content-creators-ai-bots-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweb%20crawler%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20indexes%20information%20so%20OpenAI%20can%20retrieve%20and%20show%20relevant%20results%20to%20SearchGPT%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Foriginality.ai%2Fai-bot-blocking%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOriginality.ai%3C%2Fa%3E%20tracks%20this%20stuff%20and%20it%20found%20that%2014%20of%20the%20top%201%2C000%20website%20publishers%20have%20blocked%20OAI-SearchBot.%20Other%20publications%20on%20the%20list%20include%20Wired%2C%20The%20New%20Yorker%2C%20Vogue%2C%20Vanity%20Fair%2C%20and%20GQ.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20head-scratcher%2C%20according%20to%20Jon%20Gillham%2C%20CEO%20of%20Originality.ai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20sure%20why%20any%20publisher%20would%20block%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20traffic%20that%20publishers%20want%20and%20need.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20OpenAI%20unveiled%20SearchGPT%20last%20week%20it%20stressed%20that%20OAI-SearchBot%20does%20not%20crawl%20the%20web%20to%20collect%20data%20to%20train%20its%20AI%20models%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-gpt5-gpt4-expectations-ai-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGPT-5%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20it%20advised%20website%20owners%20to%20allow%20the%20new%20bot%20to%20%26quot%3Bensure%20your%20site%20appears%20in%20search%20results.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20crawler%20access%20to%20every%20website%2C%20OpenAI's%20SearchGPT%20services%20risks%20being%20less%20complete%20than%20Google's%20Search%20engine.%20BI%20asked%20Gillham%20whether%20any%20major%20news%20publishers%20block%20Google's%20search%20bot%20and%20he%20said%20he%20doesn't%20know%20of%20any%20that%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228efd3466-d01c-454e-afa3-fa004c996e8e%5C%22%3EA%20lack%20of%20trust%2C%20or%20search%20traffic%20doubts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20another%20OpenAI%20web%20crawler%2C%20called%20GPTbot%2C%20that%20scoops%20up%20online%20data%20for%20AI%20model%20training.%20Hundreds%20of%20websites%20have%20already%20blocked%20this.%20That%20makes%20more%20sense%3A%20You%20want%20traffic%20from%20search%20engines%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20give%20away%20your%20content%20to%20train%20AI%20models%20that%20will%20likely%20compete%20against%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20OpenAI%20spent%20years%20collecting%20online%20data%20without%20permission.%20Maybe%20publishers%20just%20don't%20trust%20OpenAI%20when%20it%20says%20its%20new%20search%20bot%20won't%20also%20secretly%20suck%20up%20their%20content%20for%20AI%20training%20data%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20Gillham%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20theory%3A%20Search%20results%20these%20days%20don't%20always%20send%20users%20to%20the%20websites%20that%20worked%20hard%20to%20create%20the%20original%20content.%20Part%20of%20the%20goal%20with%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-search-generative-experience-ai-lady-gaga-sge-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI-powered%20search%20engines%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20to%20keep%20users%20around%20by%20showing%20them%20summaries.%20If%20publishers%20aren't%20seeing%20huge%20traffic%20from%20search%20engines%20anymore%2C%20why%20bother%20allowing%20their%20web%20crawling%20bots%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225df9daf4-da6f-4b1d-b82f-dc0b57415b7a%5C%22%3EA%20complaint%20from%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGillham%20also%20noted%20that%20OpenAI%20has%20been%20busy%20this%20year%20cutting%20deals%20with%20publishers%20to%20use%20their%20content%20archives.%20(Business%20Insider%20parent%20Axel%20Springer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Findex%2Faxel-springer-partnership%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esigned%20one%20of%20these%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeems%20like%20it%20was%20an%20intentional%20sequence%20of%20steps%20with%20OpenAI%2C%20first%20cozy%20up%20to%20publishers%20signing%20all%20of%20these%20partnership%20deals%20and%20then%20announcing%20SearchGPT%2C%26quot%3B%20Gillham%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20holdout%20among%20publishers%20is%20The%20New%20Yor