lions%2C%20though%20Lyles'%20exact%20net%20worth%20is%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20unsurprisingly%2C%20Lyles%20hails%20from%20a%20family%20of%20athletes.%20Both%20of%20his%20parents%20ran%20track%20and%20field%20in%20college%2C%20and%20his%20younger%20brother%2C%20Josephus%2C%20is%20also%20a%20professional%20sprinter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20love%20life%20is%20also%20on%20the%20fast%20track.%20Lyles%20is%20dating%20Jamaican%20sprinter%20Junelle%20Bromfield%2C%20who%20won%20a%20bronze%20medal%20at%20the%202020%20Tokyo%20Games%20in%20the%20women's%204%C3%97400%20meter%20relay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELyles%20lives%20in%20Florida%2C%20where%20he%20trains%20under%20coach%20Lance%20Brauman%20at%20PURE%20Athletics%20in%20Clermont.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bf822c36-0fc1-4ef8-af6e-deac8d374edc%5C%22%3ELyles%20quest%20to%20unseat%20Usain%20Bolt%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20%3Cem%3Eamong%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20fastest%20men%20in%20the%20world%20isn't%20good%20enough%20for%20Lyles.%20He%20wants%20to%20be%20%3Cem%3Ethe%3C%2Fem%3E%20fastest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20hopes%20to%20unseat%20Bolt%2C%20his%20idol%2C%20as%20the%20fastest%20man%20in%20the%20100-meter%20and%20200-meter%20races.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBolt%20set%20the%20all-time%20record%20for%20the%20200-meter%20in%202009%2C%20completing%20it%20in%2019.19%20seconds.%20Lyles%20is%20the%20third%20fastest%20man%20of%20all%20time%20with%20a%20record%20of%2019.31%20seconds%2C%20which%20he%20achieved%20in%202022%20World%20Championships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELyles%20has%20more%20ground%20to%20cover%20to%20beat%20Bolt's%20100-meter%20record%20of%209.58%20seconds.%20Ranked%20with%20the%20all-time%20fastest%20times%2C%20Lyles%20sits%20at%2015th%20compared%20to%20Bolt's%201st%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20he%20remains%20confident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20hundred%20will%20be%20a%20lot%20closer%20once%20I%20get%20the%20first%2010%20meters%20down%2C%20so%20I'd%20say%20we're%20still%20quite%20a%20few%20years%20away%20from%20that%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Olympics.com%20in%202023.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20200%3F%20Two%20years%20max.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnoah-lyles%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722627770000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668d6c2e1aace5b3ada56ef0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnoah-lyles%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20sprinter%20Noah%20Lyles%20will%20be%20competing%20in%20the%202024%20Olympics.%20Here's%20what%20to%20know%20about%20the%20career%2C%20records%2C%20and%20speed%20of%20the%20world's%20fastest%20man.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kbalevic%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Balevic)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A49%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnoah-lyles%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Harris%20campaign%20says%20it%20raised%20%24310m%20in%20July%2C%20more%20than%20double%20Trump's%20haul%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722627614000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112232875%2Cimgsize-1000392.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fharris-campaign-says-it-raised-310m-in-july-more-than-double-trumps-haul%2Farticleshow%2F112232862.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112232862.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ENeither%20campaign%20disclosed%20precisely%20how%20much%20of%20the%20money%20was%20raised%20or%20held%20by%20the%20campaigns%20themselves%20versus%20their%20allied%20party%20committees.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fharris-campaign-says-it-raised-310m-i