0sarpanch%20(village%20head).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20slate%20was%20wide%20open%20and%20I%20asked%20them%20to%20write%20on%20it%20as%20they%20wished.%20I%20gave%20them%20a%20period%20of%20three%20months%20to%20implement%20the%20project%20on%20ground%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConsidering%20their%20broad%20objective%2C%20they%20took%20most%20initiatives%20such%20as%20organising%20cleanliness%20drives%20in%20the%20village%2C%20getting%20the%20numbers%20and%20names%20fixed%20up%20on%20the%20members%20in%20the%20gram%20panchayats%2C%20organising%20meetings%20(gram%20sabhas)%2C%20and%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20girls%20started%20an%20entire%20campaign%20for%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F18554%2Fone-man-turned-village-alcohol-tobacco-free-zone%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20alcohol%20ban%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20villages.%20For%20this%2C%20they%20went%20door-to-door%20to%20motivate%20people%20and%20explain%20the%20ill-effects%20of%20consuming%20liquor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20her%20experience%20of%20conducting%20such%20a%20campaign%2C%20Mahadevi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20would%20come%20home%20drunk%20and%20cause%20trouble%20for%20members%20in%20their%20homes.%20When%20young%20girls%20explained%20how%20their%20habit%20had%20been%20impacting%20the%20upbringing%20of%20their%20children%2C%20they%20were%20ashamed.%20But%20not%20everyone%20is%20as%20understanding%2C%20many%20people%20opposed%20us.%20However%2C%20we%20remained%20undeterred.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-4-1722331581.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22These%20girls%20also%20take%20up%20initiatives%20s