E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaintaining%20the%20river%E2%80%99s%20restored%20glory%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20project%20completion%2C%20it%20was%20observed%20that%20the%20seasonal%20Sot%20river%20received%20ample%20water%20in%20the%20monsoon%20and%20remained%20rejuvenated%20for%20the%20next%20two%20and%20a%20half%20months.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20project%2C%20several%20micro%20check%20dams%20were%20also%20built%20on%20the%20river%20to%20slow%20the%20runoff%20in%20the%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20this%20work%20was%20lauded%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20his%20monthly%20radio%20programme%20%E2%80%98Mann%20Ki%20Baat%E2%80%99%20in%20September%202023.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20proved%20to%20be%20very%20encouraging%20for%20all%20the%20officials%20and%20%3Cem%3Egram%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%20associated%20with%20the%20project.%20Inspired%20by%20this%2C%20the%20districts%20of%20Amroha%20and%20Budaun%20also%20undertook%20the%20project%20of%20reviving%20the%20Sot%20river%20downstream%20and%20upstream%2C%20respectively%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Manish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-3-1722403565.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Within%20six%20months%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20revived%20the%20river%20to%20its%20old%20glory.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-3-1722403565.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-3-1722403565-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-3-1722403565-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-3-1722403565-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-3-1722403565-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359113%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWithin%20six%20months%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20revived%20the%20river%20to%20its%20old%20glory.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManish%20credits%20the%20success%20of%20the%20project%20to%20the%20local%20people%2C%20%3Cem%3Egram%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20MGNREGA%20workers%2C%20and%20district%20officials.%20In%20June%202024%2C%20he%20was%20transferred%20to%20Saharanpur%20district%20but%20this%20did%20not%20affect%20the%20success%20of%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERam%20Ashish%2C%20the%20District%20Development%20Officer%20of%20Sambhal%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20keep%20monitoring%20for%20encroachments%20and%20ensure%20that%20the%20river%20remains%20rejuvenated.%20Post%20monsoon%2C%20the%20soil%20erodes%20into%20the%20river.%20So%2C%20we%20are%20working%20on%20a%20plan%20to%20organise%20desiltation%20and%20continue%20the%20work%20started%20by%20Manish%20sir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20while%20some%20downstream%20areas%20currently%20have%20water%2C%20they%20expect%20to%20see%20the%20river%20filled%20to%20the%20brim%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20when%20it%20rains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20IAS%20Manish%20was%20reached%20out%20to%20by%20residents%20of%20Saharanpur%20to%20replicate%20the%20work%20seeing%20the%20success%20of%20the%20project%20in%20Sambhal%20district.%20%E2%80%9CSaharanpur%20has%20several%20seasonal%20rivers%20such%20as%20Kali%20and%20Hindon%20rivers.%20They%20originate%20from%20Shivaliks%20and%20pass%20through%20the%20district.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20their%20area%20has%20reduced%20in%20size.%20We%20aim%20to%20work%20on%20these%20rivers%20next%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Manish%20believes%20that%20the%20administration%20can%20only%20play%20the%20role%20of%20a%20facilitator%2C%20but%20it%20is%20only%20when%20the%20community%20becomes%20the%20protector%20of%20its%20rivers%20that%20they%20can%20remain%20rejuvenated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Manish%2C%20the%20Sot%20river%20rejuvenation%20project%20during%20his%20tenure%20in%20Sambhal%20was%20extremely%20fulfilling.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20project%20was%20very%20close%20to%20my%20heart.%20Projects%20such%20as%20river%20rejuvenation%20take%20a%20backseat%20as%20they%20are%20not%20always%20a%20priority%20among%20other%20routine%20works.%20But%20if%20we%20do%20not%20rejuvenate%20these%20rivers%2C%20people%20will%20face%20the%20brunt%20of%20a%20water%20crisis.%20Thankfully%2C%20the%20State%20Government%20has%20also%20been%20actively%20focusing%20on%20the%20environment%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F230547%2Fias-hero-kalyani-river-cleanup-uttar-pradesh-lockdown-jobs-methods-workers-inspiring-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereviving%20water%20bodies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20establishing%20Amrit%20Sarovar%20projects%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Ram%20Ashish.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722426607000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-2-1722402541.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D359103%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sot%20River%2C%20once%20the%20lifeline%20of%20Sambhal%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20lost%20its%20natural%20flow%20due%20to%20decades%20of%20encroachment.%20Here's%20how%20IAS%20Manish%20Bansal%2C%20along%20with%20officials%20and%20locals%2C%20revived%20the%20110-km%20stretch%2C%20restoring%20water%20flow%20and%20eliminating%20waterlogging.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359103%2Fias-officer-sot-river-revival-rejuvenation-project-sambhal-uttar-pradesh-manish-bansal-mgnrega-gram-panchayat-monsoon-waterlogging%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Phones%20to%20porn-blocking%20outfits%3A%20Olympians%20given%20high-tech%20swag%20for%20Paris%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722422580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F07%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-swimming-selfie_6643793.jpg%3F20240731123810%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffrom-phones-to-porn-blocking-outfits-olympic-athletes-given-high-tech-swag-for-paris-2024-13187996%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Olympic%20athletes%20have%20been%20taking%20to%20social%20media%20to%20reveal%20the%20high-tech%20swag%20they%20have%20been%20given%20for%20the%20Paris%20Olympics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffrom-phones-to-porn-blocking-outfits-olympic-athletes-given-high-tech-swag-for-paris-2024-13187996%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ffrom-phones-to-porn-blocking-outfits-olympic-athletes-given-high-tech-swag-for-paris-2024-13187996%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ffrom-phones-to-porn-blocking-outfits-olympic-athletes-given-high-tech-swag-for-paris-2024-13187996%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Designer%20Employs%20Artisan%20Families%20To%20Handcraft%20Brass%2C%20Copper%20Kitchenware%3B%20Earns%20Rs%2036%20Cr%2FYear%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20find%20their%20calling%20early%20in%20life%20and%20remain%20dedicated%20to%20their%20childhood%20dreams%20of%20becoming%20doctors%2C%20teachers%2C%20and%20more.%20However%2C%20for%20some%2C%20discovering%20their%20passion%20takes%20time%20and%20multiple%20attempts.%20This%20was%20true%20for%20Kirti%20Goel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20life%20decisions%2C%